g.text: UC2 - Specifies type of vaccine to be administer
UC4 - Comfirm the vaccination is schedule and informs the user
UC5 - Sends to the user an SMS confirming the vaccination event
UC6 - Configures and manages the core information: vaccines, type of vaccines, vaccination centers, employes
UC7 - Registers arrival of SNS user
UC8 - Confirms information about SNS user
UC9 - Check user infor and health condition
UC11 - Registers vaccination andministration with vaccine type
UC12 - Record adverse reactions on the system
UC13 - Request EU COVID digital certificate
UC15 - Sends user notification SMS or Email
UC16 - Verifies user recovery time is over
